name: Caldwell - Antoinette Culerba Lanceros - Antoinette Culebra Lanceros
additionalNotes: This Caldwell Crafted and Curated Antoinete Culebra Twists cigar is made in Dominican Republic and contains 3 Lancero cigars twisted together to make a beautiful creation. Made at El Maestro, these amazing cigars are made with Ecuadorian Habano wrapper with Binder and Fillers from the Dominician Republic. This cigar is one of the fabulous experiments produce by Robert Caldwell himself.Â
